<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fira+Code:wght@300;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <title>Document</title>
</head>
<style>
  body {
    color: #beb9b3;
    font-family: "Fira Code", monospace;
    padding: 0;
    border: 0;
    margin: 0 auto;
    background: #1a1c1c;
    max-width: 980px;
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  main {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  header {
    width: 100%;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 10px;
    background: #141516;
    min-height: 45px;
    height: 45px;
    max-height: 60px;
  }

  header img {
    width: 5%;
    min-width: 50px;
  }

  button {
    outline: none;
    border: none;
    background: #62b6cb;
    height: 50px;
    min-height: 50px;
    width: 200px;
    color: white;
    font-weight: bold;
    font-size: larger;
    border-radius: 15px;
  }

  section {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-evenly;
    width: 62%;
    height: 75vh;
  }

  .welcome {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
  }

  footer {
    width: 100%;
    background: #141516;
    height: 100px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  footer img {
    width: 10%;
    max-width: 100px;
    min-width: 60px;
  }
</style>

<body>
  <main>
    <header>
      <img width="25%"
        src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dvtoxwpe7/image/upload/v1593404411/ic_launcher-playstore_tnoqwd.png"
        alt="Logo" />
    </header>
    <section>
      <h2>ESQUECEU SUA SENHA?</h2>
      <p>
        <span class="welcome">Olá, {{username}}<br /></span>
        Houve uma solicitação de redefinição de senha. Se você não solicitou
        esta redefinição de senha, ignore este e-mail. Caso contrário, clique
        no botão abaixo para alterar sua senha
      </p>
      <button>Redefinir senha</button>
    </section>
  </main>
  <footer>
    <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dvtoxwpe7/image/upload/v1593407894/ic_logo_z7vbum.png" alt="Full logo" />
  </footer>
</body>

</html>
